<br>
The Barbarians of Halas are amiable. This is helpful because spell prices in Shar Vahl are very high. It is worth the time to travel to Halas for spell purchases once you are able.<br>
<br>
By using Sneak, you can get behind a merchant and have him regard you indifferently regardless of faction. This allows you to get better prices if the merchant is ordinarily apprehensive. Dubious merchants won't trade at all unless you sneak up behind them.<br>
<br>
There are no deity selections for Vah Shir. We are all Agnostic.<br>
<br>
